{"tid":2402699,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★平機會呼籲僱主勿作種族及殘疾歧視行為!","createTime":"2021-02-10T14:51:10.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-11T05:10:40.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"90da2ac4c9e66a1a3512d073d6a1c369ea03fbd3","tid":2402699,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T14:51:10.000Z","msg":"平機會表示，近日接獲不同團體反映及個別求助査詢，指有南亞裔建造業工人被僱主基於其種族背景指令停工，即使取得新冠檢測陰性結果，但未能如華裔及其他族裔員工般可返回地盤工作。平機會提醒僱主，<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>切勿針對僱員的種族背景，作出違法的種族歧視和殘疾歧視行為</strong></span>。<br />\n<br />\n平機會主席朱敏健表示，平機會希望社會時刻保持理性，避免作出分化、製造社會矛盾和歧視性的言論及行為，亦呼籲僱主，應對所有員工採取一視同仁的政策，切勿針對僱員的種族背景，作出違法的種族歧視和殘疾歧視行為。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2876610/【新冠肺炎】平機會接獲求助指南亞裔建築工遭停工%E3%80%80呼籲僱主勿作種族及殘疾歧視行為?mtc=10012\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2876610%2F%E3%80%90%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E%E3%80%91%E5%B9%B3%E6%A9%9F%E6%9C%83%E6%8E%A5%E7%8D%B2%E6%B1%82%E5%8A%A9%E6%8C%87%E5%8D%97%E4%BA%9E%E8%A3%94%E5%BB%BA%E7%AF%89%E5%B7%A5%E9%81%AD%E5%81%9C%E5%B7%A5%25E3%2580%2580%E5%91%BC%E7%B1%B2%E5%83%B1%E4%B8%BB%E5%8B%BF%E4%BD%9C%E7%A8%AE%E6%97%8F%E5%8F%8A%E6%AE%98%E7%96%BE%E6%AD%A7%E8%A6%96%E8%A1%8C%E7%82%BA%3Fmtc%3D10012&d=9j7BdtwWq97OJFdF2FXGhf4XLRjZdTHGp6sdrEQ6olc%3D&h=bf3a6bde\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2876610/【新冠肺炎】平機會接獲求助指南亞裔建築工遭停工%E3%80%80呼籲僱主勿作種族及殘疾歧視行為?mtc=10012</a>"},{"pid":"7a153e35bef665076a40f34363aefeea5e056de3","tid":2402699,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T14:51:28.000Z","msg":"支族<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca6fe7bcdeb44648c88d6131c22e50763d5d6a39","tid":2402699,"uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T14:51:56.000Z","msg":"呢個？<br />\n<br />\n<br 